                          and complexity versus\nperformance).  I don't have any absolute
                          figures to hand, but you\nshould be able to find references
                          on rec.games.mud.lp and *.pike.\n\n--\nJ C Lawrence                                 Home:
                          claw@kanga.nu\n----------(*)                              Other:
